BUT what’s happening in Palestine today is out of mind, I cannot believe we are witnessing genocide in 2023!! where did all the education go? Our so called intellectual.. that it’s taking us 26 days to pick a side!! This is not a WAR to pick a side, This is a genocide happening in front of your eyes and you’re watching it on your screen 24/7 and totally ignoring it. Families, school, and anything you name it in G@Z@ has been destoried!! you just have to have a heart ceasefire NOW!! 

This genocide will forever be written in history!
